# Wave-5 review — the frontend image builds with context ./frontend, so
# the ROOT .dockerignore does not apply here. Without this file a local
# `docker-compose build` COPYs the host's node_modules over the image's
# freshly `npm ci`-installed one (host-platform native binaries → build
# failure or non-lockfile deps) and bloats the context with artefacts.
node_modules
dist
coverage
